Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:22.93,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re a genius, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.81,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…I actually practiced for three whole days though…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.95,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh? Didja say something?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:30.40,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing! It’s nothing!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Alright, now it’s your turn, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna teach you reaaaal good now.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
