Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:54.26,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Huh!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:56.31,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You’re changing schools, Ruri-chan!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:00.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I don’t want this…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:05.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to leave you, Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you forever…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:11.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Three days ‘til the performance…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:31.21,Rurino,,0,0,0,,This time for sure, Megu-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:35.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,We’ll captivate the whole world…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:40.43,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve practiced my singing and dancing really hard, and I’ve been doing lots of stamina training!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:47.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,All that’s left is to get up on stage and work {\i1}very, very{\i0} hard… but…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Haah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Will I be okay…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:59.70,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If my battery dies during the performance, then…  {\fad(0,300)}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:04.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s it.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.95,Rurino,,0,0,0,,‘kay, bye…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.25,Megumi,,0,0,0,,R-Ruri-chan…!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.70,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’d be a total disaster! Super bad!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.42,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But there’s nothing I could do about it!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should install some solar panels on myself!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:31.33,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Rain, rain, goooo… away!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.48,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Ruri-chan?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:45.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,M-Making weather charms…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.55,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Okay…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.49,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it makes sense that you’d want good weather when you perform.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:51.87,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, what are you doing here, Megu-chan?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.70,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you feel like coming back to the club!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.77,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Noooope!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:03.16,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Just here to return the notebook I borrowed from Kozue~.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.35,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:08.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I guess you’re still not good at studying…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:13.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,It’s only when it’s for school!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I just can’t seem to score well on tests.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And that’s why they enrolled you into Hasunosora, huh~\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:25.14,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Just when my showbiz career was popping off, too!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:30.45,Megumi,,0,0,0,,They told me to get a proper education and shipped me off to this dorm!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.84,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I thought my life was so over!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.96,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan, can you spell “anemone”?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:41.98,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You think I’m stupid?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.98,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Of course I can…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.48,Megumi,,0,0,0,,A- N-… Y-……\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.24,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Whatever, it’s too hard!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.81,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:55.10,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Your performance is coming up pretty soon, right?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:56.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.54,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re gonna come watch, right, Megu-chan?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:01.54,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I guess…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But are you gonna be okay?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh, what do you mean?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:15.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, I guess I made it seem like I wasn’t ready yet back at the training camp, but still!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.94,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve been working on it!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:25.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And also, Kozue-senpai and Tsuzuri-senpai have been super nice! \NIt was honestly surprising how nice they are!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.95,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Nah, that’s not what I mean.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:32.44,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m talking about how fast you tire out when you’re with other people.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.36,Rurino,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:41.47,Megumi,,0,0,0,,So I was just wondering if you’d actually be able to perform in front of all those people.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:47.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,L-Listen! I got a lot of buffs during my time abroad!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.87,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m waaay stronger than I was back then!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Really now~.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:59.64,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But if there’s a chance you might mess up, wouldn’t it be better to get some more practice in?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No problem!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:09.49,Rurino,,0,0,0,,My special, {\i1}marvelous{\i0} performance will definitely make you feel much better, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.59,Megumi,,0,0,0,,About that…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:17.90,Megumi,,0,0,0,,If you’re really doing this performance for my sake, don’t.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:28.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m glad you feel that way, and I really am looking forward to seeing you perform, but…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:35.18,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry to say this, but I doubt I’d be able to return to the stage even after that.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Why would you say something like that!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’ll be fine! I’ll be giving it my all!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.98,Megumi,,0,0,0,,There are things that even hard work can’t achieve…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:50.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Even back when I stopped contacting you, I did whatever I could to try to come back.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:55.82,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I tried and tried, but in the end, nothing ended up working.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.44,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I tried going to performances from school idols I liked.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:02.01,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I tried helping Kozue and Tsuzuri.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:04.01,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I tried doing physical therapy.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.72,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But nothing changed.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:11.28,Megumi,,0,0,0,,At this point, I doubt even seeing you perform would…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.42,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Are…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:20.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Are you saying all that because you’re worried I might run out of battery during the performance…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.28,Megumi,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.41,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I just don’t want you to waste your effort on nothing.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.20,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But we won’t know if it’ll be a waste until we try!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:32.38,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting this way!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:38.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Is it because you don’t like school idols anymore!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.82,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Again, no!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:46.78,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I just want you to be a school idol for {\i1}yourself{\i0}, not for me.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:51.42,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m sure you’ll have so much fun if you do, so…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:55.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I want to be a school idol with {\i1}you{\i0}!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.67,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You’re so annoying!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.38,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Fine, I’ll just go out and say it, then!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:03.01,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m tired of being a school idol!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.18,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I started doing it just to kill time!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.87,Megumi,,0,0,0,,There, are you happy now!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.66,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Is that what you wanted!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You’re lying!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.39,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I mean, you sounded so happy on the phone…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:26.78,Megumi,,0,0,0,,This time for sure, we’ll be able to captivate the whole world as school idols!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:31.85,Megumi,,0,0,0,,C’mon, Ruri-chan! Hurry and come to Hasunosora, already–\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.74,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Stupid Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:41.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,No matter what you tell me, I’m not giving up!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.37,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Not until…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:47.54,Rurino,,0,0,0,,not until the two of us are school idols together!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.74,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Stupid!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.03,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Ruri-chan…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.80,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You’re the stupid one…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:08:01.99,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Why… Why are you doing this much, just for me…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.95,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Did… something happen?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.75,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Ruri sprinted out of the room just now…\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Megu?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:17.65,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.59,Megumi,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no, it was nothing!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:27.10,Megumi,,0,0,0,,W-We just had a little bit of an argument, but everything’s all… okay…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.24,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Oh, those shoes.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:33.80,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Hm?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.90,Megumi,,0,0,0,,So you still have them in here, huh.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:44.80,Megumi,,0,0,0,,They’ve been collecting dust for a year now, so you probably should’ve just thrown them away.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:51.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…But you haven’t given up on becoming a school idol yet.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:56.09,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We thought you’d come back someday.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:57.91,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:02.10,Megumi,,0,0,0,,yeah.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:06.54,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Kozue… Tsuzuri…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:12.50,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I… I’m so frustrated…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.48,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan said all those things to me, but…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:25.35,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Whenever I close my eyes, I’m back under those spotlights, and I can’t move…  \N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:44.33,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I tried to dance so many times, but I just couldn’t.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:50.63,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Even though you two were always there for me, it still didn’t work…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:59.72,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And then I’d ruin the performance, and you’d have to try really hard to cover for me…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:07.12,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And I know that I should’ve just quit, that I should’ve given up…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:13.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,All because of these… these worthless…!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi, you shouldn’t hit your legs like that–\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.35,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Especially now that they’re better…\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.21,Megumi,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.63,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m always so frustrated…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:31.07,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Why…? Why can’t I dance on stage anymore…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:36.16,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What… should I even do…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:42.87,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Is there really… no other option for me…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.34,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna do my best.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,
